Product name: Antique Victorian engraved Sterling silver buckle bracelet 925
Description:
This stunning antique bracelet jewelry is an antique Victorian buckle bracelet in Sterling silver.  The engraving s beautiful, featuring a bird, which is a popular Victorian motif.  There is a blank area on back which I believe might have been left open to have perhaps a name engraved, but luckily, none was ever added!  There is also another area on the front by the bird which might work well if you wanted to have a loved one's initials engraved at your local jewelers, turning it into a wonderful family keepsake!
The bracelet is Sterling silver and as you can see in the photos, is quality stamped.  It measures 7 1/2" in circumference, so for someone who's wrist measures say 7 1/4" around or less.
This  bracelet does have a buckle clasp, but it is not adjustable to different sizes. It does have a hing and opens and closes to put it on, so unlike a bangle that you hav to be able to get over your hand, this opens to put on at the wrist.  This makes the bracelet ideal for gift giving, as long as you approximately know the measurement around the wrist.
I do have som additional pictures available if you need them, please message me and I can send them....I am only allowed the 5 pictures in my listing.

Product name: Basil Mandarin Tea Light Candles - earthy candles - scented candles - scented tea lights
Description:
Basil Mandarin gives off a clean, fresh scent with an earthy aroma. 6 tealights per box.
Notes:  Lime, basil, amber, mandarin, moss, patchouli.
We are constantly busy with how fast paced and convoluted the modern world can be. A tea light is a small and simple piece that can break through the chaos and create a calming space to take a step back. It gives us a peaceful atmosphere that offers simplicity and in a world that constantly barrages our senses. A tea light candle holds the sophistication and elegance of a regular candle, while adding a luxuriously private and personal feeling in its small size.
- Created with quality fragrance oil and premium soy and paraffin blend for the clean burn of soy and great scent throw of paraffin with lead and zinc free cotton wicks.
- Tealight comes in heat resistant, clear polycarbonate containers that are recyclable and measure 1.5” wide and 0.75” tall. 
- Hand packaged in a box of 6, each tealight burns up to 5 hours.
- Products meet ASTM quality and safety standard.
- Wax is dye-free with smooth, opaque and creamy appearance.
- Each tealight is poured and wicked by hand, one candle at a time, to ensure quality and performance.
- Free shipping with no minimum purchase. 
Safety Tips:
• The best option to hold tealight candles are holders that are specifically made for tealight candles. Similarly sized holder will keep tealights from moving around and therefore provide a safe burning environment.
• Clear cup tealights are not to be used in enclosed or covered tealight holders such as tart burners, tealight houses, and lamps. The heat can build up inside an enclosed holder and melt the clear cup. These candles are for open style holders.
• Keep trimming the wick to ¼ inches. A longer wick leads to a larger flame which is more dangerous than a smaller flame.
• Keep the candle away from drafts. Drafts can create an uneven burn and excessive smoke.
• Keep the candle away from flammable objects. Do not place the candle near curtains or other fabrics or beneath anything that can catch fire.
• Avoid placing a tealight on top of a plastic surface, even if it is in a holder. The heat still runs the risk of producing a fire.
• Keep the candle away from children and pets. Accidents can happen!
• Never leave burning candles unattended. Keep them within sight at all times.

Product name: 18" Memory Bear / Keepsake Bear from Adult Clothes **PLEASE Read Item Details for Info**
Description:
My current turn around time is 10-12 weeks from when I receive your items, not your order date. Thank you for your patience and understanding! 😊
This listing is for the 18" Memory Bear / Keepsake Bear from Adult Clothes ONLY. I do make the 18" Memory Bear / Keepsake Bear from Baby Clothes also. If you are looking for those, this link will take you there:
 
https://www.etsy.com/listing/229806717/18-memory-bear-keepsake-bear-from-baby
 
 -For additions to your bear, see the "Additional Options" link within this listing. 
I love the idea of being able to carry a loved one with you. These "one of a kind" memory bears are perfect for those who have had a loved one pass away and would like a bear made in their honor.
I make your special bear from clothing that you send me.
A bear can be made from one men's medium shirt or larger, or women's large or larger. You can send more than one shirt if you want them mixed together. If what you want to use is a youth size or a women's x-small, small or medium, I will need two shirts per bear.
Some great ideas from adult clothing are:
***Non Stretch Fabrics*** :
-Button down shirts
-Flannel shirts
-Flannel pajamas
-Fleece shirts
-Fleece pajamas
-Flannel or Fleece bath robes (knee length or longer)
-Cotton dresses (knee length or longer)
-Cotton skirts (knee length or longer)
-Corduroy items - pants or jackets
-Denim items - jeans or jackets
-Uniform shirts
***Stretchy Fabrics*** :
-T-shirts (please keep in mind that if there is a large logo on your t-shirt, that it may not all fit on your bear)
-Golf/Polo shirts
-Sweatshirts (please keep in mind that if there is a large logo on your sweatshirt, that it may not all fit on your bear)
-Cotton knit/t-shirt dresses (knee length or longer)
-Cotton knit skirts (knee length or longer)
With items that are stretchy, I iron in an easy knit stabilizer to help control stretching and maintain shape.
If you have specific items you would like to use other than what is listed above, please contact me BEFORE placing your order.
Materials that can't be used:
-loose knit items
-handmade crochet or knit items
-sheer or lace items
-silky or thin satin items (like night gowns or blouses)
-nylon or nylon blend items
I sometimes use your item's buttons for the eyes and a small piece of felt for the nose. If there are no buttons to use, I will use safety eyes. I try to use any emblem or logo from the shirt if it will fit onto your bear (unless specified not to). The neck is double stitched (since it's the part that gets the most lovin' 😉). 
Additional Options - If you would like any additions to your bear (such as: a ribbon bow around the neck, bow or bow tie, fabric tag, embroidery, or a neck tag), please see this separate listing for "Additional Options". These options will need to be purchased IN ADDITION TO your memory bear.
 
https://www.etsy.com/listing/223204350/additional-options-to-purchase-for
 
To see all of my memory items and other listings, please visit my shop at:
 www.MySewWhatShop.etsy.com 
ORDERING PROCESS:
1. Add this listing to your cart by selecting shirt/fabric type, number of items used per bear, and the number of bears you would like to order.
2. If there are any additions you would like with your bear (ribbon bow, bow or bow tie, fabric tag, etc.), add those to your cart too. 
3. Check out. Once I receive your order confirmation, I will send you an Etsy convo with the address you will need to send your item(s) to.
-Please send your items to me within a week of placing your order. This helps keep your order within the estimated turn around time given in your order confirmation.
-Please be kind and wash all items before they are sent to me. It is GREATLY appreciated! Items with heavy odors will be returned to you using the shipping cost from your order, and your order will be cancelled. This is not meant to be taken offensively, but I work very closely with these items and appreciate your taking the time to freshly launder your items I'll be working with. Thank you!!
-Please be sure to put your FIRST and LAST NAME on your package. If you send your item(s) from a business address or without your name, it takes me a lot of time to figure out who the items belong to.
4. When I receive your items, I will Etsy convo you to let you know they have arrived here safe and sound.
5. You will get an Etsy convo from me the week I have your order lined up to work on.
6. You will get an email with your tracking information when your order is on it's way to you.
Care Instructions: It is recommended to spot clean your bear with a mild soap or detergent. Air dry. 
NOTICE: While every care is taken to make your bear safe and strong, it is intended as a keepsake only. Should you wish to give this to a child for gentle play, that is your decision, and therefore your responsibility to supervise their play, as small plastic parts are used.
**The bears in this listing are not for sale. They are examples only.**

Product name: Fine Silver Tar Valon Mark  on Amyrlin letter, Wheel of Time officially licensed merchandise.
Description:
This was struck  in 1/4 troy ounce (8 grams) of pure .999 silver. These coins were made using ancient techniques, so Each coin is unique due to that we used a silver ball to make the coin. These coins have a non uniform rim with some cracking. The obverse features the face of Siuan Sanche, holding a flame on her open palm, flanked by seven stars and wearing the stole of the Amyrlin Seat, striped with seven colors. The reverse side features the ancient symbol of the Ourobouros, the snake eating it’s own tail, used to symbolize eternity and the Wheel of Time. In the center of the reverse side is the Flame of Tar Valon, official symbol and seal of the White Tower and the Amyrlin Seat. The letter reads: 
"What the bearer does is done at my order and by my authority  Obey and keep silent, at my command. 
 Siuan Sanche 
Watcher of the Seals 
Flame of Tar Valon 
The Amyrylin Seat
The framable document with coin comes in a 9″ x 11.5″ hard plastic top-loader sleeve for protection..
 Each order comes witha  custom certificate of authenticity. 
Based on The Wheel of Time™ series by Robert Jordan.  We have officially licensed with Bandersnatch Inc. to produce the coins that would exist in the world defined by Robert Jordan’s fictional works. This is our second entry in the series.
In the tale, the Amyrlin Seat provided documents on rare occasions to individuals in her service. The master copy of the document was calligraphed by Renee Troy, and bears these words: “What the bearer does is done at my order and by my authority. Obey and keep silent at my command.”
These coins were designed here at Shire Post Mint, approved by the Bandersnatch Group, and struck here at our own facility in Arkansas. The obverse die featuring the face of the Amyrlin Seat, was hand-engraved by master-engraver Ron Landis, widely known for his work with Gallery Mint Museum. The coin blanks are individually melted and flattened, such that each individual coin is unique… some even showing cracks and flaws at the edge just like many ancient real-world silver coins.
Here at Shire Post Mint we are dedicated to the principle of creating artifacts from worlds of fiction and mythology in order to create tactile touch-pieces to help fans immerse into their beloved fantasy worlds. We work closely with authors (or their heirs) and highly skilled numismatists and die-engravers to create pieces with the utmost of authenticity.
My name is Tom Maringer and I make fantasy coins under the trade name Shire Post Mint. These  coins (or "tokens") are made here in my workshop in Arkansas. There are now five people working here, but I still run the main press at least part of the time to maintain quality control.

Product name: THE SPAMP Guitar Practice Amplifier And Distortion Effect
Description:
THE SPAMP is a guitar preamplifier, distortion effect and headphone practice amplifier in a conveniently sized enclosure which can be free standing or clipped on to your belt.  The circuit is an original design, not a clone of any stomp box and not designed to emulate any particular sound.  
The main signal path is a distributed gain JFET amplifier. The very high input impedance presents minimal loading to the pick-up resulting in a wide, flat passband which sounds great. There is no tone or EQ control – use the control on your guitar or amplifier head.
SPICE adjusts the gain prior to the distortion stage.  This controls the amount or harshness of the distortion.  
HEAT adjusts the post distortion signal level going on to your amp or following effects.
CHILLED no distortion, just the warm tone of JFET amplification.  You can of course persuade a distorted output in CHILLED mode by winding up SPICE and or HEAT! 
FRIED a subtle application of even harmonics for a warm fuzz.
GRILLED introduces odd harmonics for a meatier overdrive distortion. 
LINE IN    a 3.5mm socket intended for connection to a line or headphone level source from a mobile phone or other media player. A 3.5mm stereo male – male cable is supplied for this. The stereo input is mixed into a mono signal and added to the guitar output path.  This is a unity gain buffered pass-through, it won't boost the volume of your iPhone!  Use the volume control on your media player to adjust the output level of the mixed in source.  
‘PHONES  a 3.5mm output socket. THE SPAMP is optimised to drive headphones with a nominal impedance of at 16 to 32 ohms.  
The amplified guitar output is mixed with left and right channels of the headphone output so you can play along without disturbing your parents / partner / children as applicable.
Using THE SPAMP 
First of all, open the battery compartment and carefully connect a 9V battery to the clip. Try not to strain the wires. If pulled excessively they might break or be pulled off the circuit board. THE SPAMP has reverse polarity protection so don’t worry if you momentarily connect the battery backwards. 
THE SPAMP is energised only when a ¼ inch jack is inserted into the input socket. At risk of teaching you to suck eggs (which go well with Spam®) make sure the HEAT control is fully anticlockwise (low gain) and that there is preferably a guitar on the other end of the lead. If you plug in an open lead and the gain is wound up with an amp or headphones attached, you are likely to get a good, loud dose of mains hum. 
When THE SPAMP is activated, the yellow LED will glow. 
If a ¼ inch jack is inserted in the output socket, the headphone amp is automatically switched off to preserve battery life.  The output impedance is lower than 1 kohm and will have no difficulty driving following effects or your stack.  
When you use THE SPAMP for the first time, introduce it gradually to your guitar and amp. Start off with SPICE and HEAT set to about 9 O’clock – roughly 25% gain. Likewise, turn your guitar down to about halfway and your amp to something that won’t freak your cat / dog / neighbours, etc.
Play around with the settings on your guitar and THE SPAMP.  
THE SPAMP is equally happy with single coil or hum-bucker pick-ups.  Experiment to get the best sound with your set-set up.  Try it with the neck pick-up selected and the guitar tone turned right the way down for that old fashioned overdrive sound.  
The SPAMP Story
Early one morning, before bed time, in about 2001, Spamp Man returned from a gig feeling somewhat peckish. Enraptured by the ensuing Spam® sandwich, Spamp Man received the inspiration for the Spicy Amplifier, THE SPAMP. A prototype was knocked up using the very can that provided the meal of enlightenment. And there the story might have ended but, in 2016, Spamp Man decided to share THE SPAMP with the World...
THE SPAMP was designed by SPAMP MAN and all SPAMPs are assembled to a professional standard and 100% tested by SPAMP MAN himself.  
Shipping
All SPAMPs are shipped by Royal Mail 1st class signed-for in the UK and by Royal Mail Tracked and Signed overseas.  Orders should be shipped within 3 days of receipt and will be confirmed.   
COMING SOON!  
THE STAMP - all the meaty goodness of THE SPAMP in a stomp - box.

Description:
Maximize Space 
Minimize Effort 
Wanna Know How These Work? Check It Out on our store home page.
What is this product:
 Most of the time when corn hole boards are made to be portable they lose their quality. This collapsible option keeps the quality of the board enacted while making them portable. These are corn hole boards that can collapse so that they are the width of one corn hole board. Shipping:

Color:
If you order this product it is strictly raw with no finish, if you would like to purchase painted or stained corn hole boards please see the painted corn hole boards posting. 
Why we created this product:
Cornhole is a great game for the summer and football seasons, but once the winter hit and we had to put the cornhole boards away they became a nuisance. We created these cornhole boards for this reason. We can play with them during the summer and fall. But once it is time to put them away we can store them away without taking up as much space.

Product name: Vintage batik guitar strap -- shades of aqua, peach and black
Description:
The fabric of this strap is a vintage Indonesian batik sarong fabric. I bought the fabric in the 1980s and only had one length of it, so only a very small number of these straps can be made. The colours are shades of blue-green/aqua and peach on a black background, with a pattern of stylised flowers. This fabric is 100% cotton, which gives the strap a lot of stability to hold its shape as well as being comfortable to wear and stunning to look at.
As a musician you create beauty in the form of melody, harmony and rhythm, and connect with people through emotion, passion and joy. I make my straps with a similar attention to the harmonious balance of aesthetics, form and function. They are made by hand in my home studio on the rural outskirts of Sydney, Australia. Whether you’re looking for a new strap for yourself, or as a gift for someone else, you will know that a MyMumDrivesaUFO strap has been made by someone who is doing what they love. 
My straps are very comfortable, strong and hard-wearing. They feature: 
•	Hand-shaped and hole-punched black leather ends
•	2inch wide black polypropylene webbing (rated to 250kg breaking strength)
•	100% cotton fabric, lined with medium weight fusible interfacing to add a layer of softness and cushioning
•	chrome-coloured metal adjustment fittings
•	length adjustable to approximately 154cm (60 inches) 
I do my best to ensure that the photos of the straps accurately reflect their colours. However, computer screens can vary in their reproduction of colours. If absolute colour accuracy is important to you, message me to request a fabric sample before purchase.

Product name: Basic LED Bike frame lighting kit, LED Bike Kit, Bike Lighting, Bike Light, Super Bright LED kit.
Description:
We can custom make everything to your specifications and ship it to you with USPS Priority Mail. Everything is made in-house, to meet your individualized needs with the highest quality materials available. All the kits we sell have a 30 day warranty against manufacturing defects. So if it breaks ship it back to us and if we can't repair it, it will be replaced.
We are a brand new start up company designed with the client in mind. I personally bike 40 miles a day in every weather condition and I know what will and won't hold up. We have been sampling various products and have come up with a great frame lighting solution. We are confident that you won't find another product with the same quality workmanship at such an affordable price.
We aim to please and have come up with a very wide selection of parts and accessories that will help you make your bike stand out in the dark. Most of our kits are installed in as little as 20 minutes. Each kit includes everything you will need to install it, except the batteries. Also included with every kit is a professional install guide with step by step direction and a quick-start guide for the electrically inclined. You can visit out website for more pics and video too. http://www.ledbikekit.net
We take PayPal payments over the web and if you don't have PayPal, we can take your credit card order over the phone. 
Our LED Bike Kit
	
Basic Kit Includes: http://ledbikekit.net/component_pics.html
1x 12v Battery Holder (used with 8AA Batteries @ 1.5v/each)
1x Pack of assorted Zip Ties (10x 8", 10x 11")
1x Wiring Harness and LED Controller
2x 18" Extension Cables or 2x 24" Extension Cables
4x 12" LED Strips (choose your colors: red,green,blue,white,yellow)
1x Quick Start Guide with step by step installation instructions
1x Velcro Carrying Case
Though you see 8 strips on the mountain bike in the pics above, it is using our advanced kit which comes with double the LED Strips(8) and a different controller that has 8 outputs. If you would like that please contact us and let us know what strip colors you want. You can see videos and more pics on our website. If you are inclined you can install these on your motorcycles with ease as I have done for lots of people. But we are advertising them here on Etsy as Bicycle frame kits. They are 12 volt and if put on a motorcycle will need an inline fuse and a switch. The double sided mounting tape is just for positioning. You need to use the included zip ties to make sure your led strips stay on your bike.
Please email us with any questions.  sales [!at] ledbikekit.net.
WHEN YOU PURCHASE YOUR KIT, PLEASE INCLUDE WHAT 4 STRIP COLORS YOU WANT.
WE HAVE RED,GREEN,BLUE,WHITE, AND YELLOW. If no color is specified we will ship white/red, which is the brightest for night time visibility.

✦ ABOUT GOLD FILLED ✦
✧ Gold filled is an actual layer of gold-pressure bonded to another metal.
✧ Gold filled does not flake off, rub off or turn colors.
✧ Most people with jewelry sensitivities can wear gold filled without worries of any allergic reaction.
✧ Heirloom jewelry from the 1800’s is often gold-filled which gives us confidence that it will last a lifetime!
____________________________________________
✦ GOLD FILLED CARE ✦
✧ Warm water and a soft cloth are the best thing you can do to maintain the beauty of your jewelry.
✧ Jewelry polishing cloths work great and are non-abrasive.
✧ For a deeper, occasional cleaning, a drop of dish soap on a toothbrush will return its luster.
✧ Salt water and chlorine in swimming pools take their toll on all fine jewelry.
✧ Many chemicals marketed for cleaning jewelry are actually somewhat abrasive or corrosive and can cause damage or color alteration to your jewelry.

Description:
Hand forged iron bracelets. Set of three 
Dramatic and sure to be noticed...each bracelet is handmade by me in a coal forge, shaped on the anvil, brushed, and finished with wax to prevent rusting and add shine.
I now have three sizing options available... Please take the time to measure as these cannot be bent. I recommend taking a bracelet that fits you and measuring it across the middle.
Small: diameter of 2.5 inches - 8 inch circumference
Medium: diameter of 2.75 inches - 8 1/2 inch circumference
Large: diameter of 3 inches - 9 inch circumference
***Please note that you will need a larger size for this bangle Since it is a closed bangle, it has to fit over your hand.***
The important measurement is that it is able to slide over the hand without bending. Keep in mind the circumference of these is larger than wrist size to accommodate for that.  A good way to figure out your size is to grab a piece of string and squish your hand down (as if you're preparing to pass a bangle over it) take the string and wrap it around the biggest part of your hand and measure it very tightly. Then compare that measurement to the sizing above and select the bangle that works best for you.  Also, if you are buying for someone else and it's a gift, the most common size is medium. If you're unsure it's always best to go bigger than smaller.
I am available to do custom sizes. Please contact me with any requests.
